data.description: Welcome to the Aston Lakes community of Winter Haven, Florida, where this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home awaits you. Situated in a tranquil gated 55+ neighborhood, this residence offers a desirable open floor plan, creating a welcoming and spacious atmosphere for both everyday living and entertaining.    As you step into the home, you'll be greeted by the seamless flow between the living, dining, and kitchen areas, enhancing the sense of connectivity. In this stunning kitchen, elegance meets functionality. The space is adorned with expansive granite countertops as well as beautiful cabinets that not only provide ample storage but also serve as a focal point, showcasing a timeless design. The refrigerator, oven, microwave, and dishwasher stand as sleek, elements that not only elevate the kitchen's visual appeal but also offer top-notch performance for all your culinary needs.    Luxurious owner's suite featuring expansive windows that flood the space with natural light, complemented by a well appointed bathroom boasting a separate soaking tub and shower. This indulgent retreat is further enhanced by the convenience of dual walk-in closets.    Another standout feature of this property is the screened-in lanai, providing a perfect retreat for relaxation. The spacious lanai includes a large hot tub, offering an ideal spot to unwind after a long day or entertain guests in a private setting.    For those with a passion for golf, the home boasts a 2-car garage with an additional golf cart garage, allowing for convenient storage of your golfing essentials.    The Aston Lakes community itself adds to the appeal of this home, with its well-appointed clubhouse serving as a central hub for various recreational amenities. Some amenities that residents can enjoy are the convenience of a fitness center to maintain an active lifestyle, both an outdoor oversized refreshing pool for hot Florida days as well as an indoor oversized heated pool for those cooler Florida days, a multi-purpose room for community events and gatherings, a movie theater, an on-site restaurant as well as two 18-hole golf courses.    Outdoor enthusiasts will appreciate the tennis and pickleball courts, providing opportunities for friendly matches and socializing with neighbors. To complete the experience, a relaxing hot tub is available within the community, offering a serene space to enjoy the Florida weather.    In summary, this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in the Aston Lakes community is not just a residence; it's a lifestyle. With its open floor plan, screened lanai with a hot tub, and access to a range of community amenities, it offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and leisure in the heart of Winter Haven, Florida.
